## 🚀Pod

```bash
kubectl run my-nginx --image=nginx --port=80 --env="ENV=PROD" --labels="app=nginx-app,env=prod"
```

Common Flags:

- `--restart`= `Always`(Default), `OnFailure`, `Never`
- `--command -- sleep 3600`

